<br>
I'm all for trying to fit the image you have in your mind, but for me personally, my image was costing my friends experience and wasting much of their time.  I decided that wasn't a sacrifice I was going to force on them any longer when my own vanity was the cause.<br>
<br>
Once I can get a nice one hand weapon, I'll gladly switch to it and look for a really nice shield to compliment it, but as it stands, no shield is worth going to a sub-par 1H like SoTM unless you need the resists for a Dragon type raid.  Even then, you aren't helping the raid much with the little damage you contribute unless you are main tanking it.<br>
<br>
